Date: Wed, 1 Jul 2026 20:59:30 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 03/22] Add persistent TermSurf Ladybird ABI handles

The one-shot bird learned not to flee,
It keeps a perch for Rust and C.
Views now linger, pumps now tick,
And bad calls fail politely quick.
